---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="jrgmadrid"
  description="after-hours editorial. senior dev, vancouver, between things."
>
  <main class="spread">

    <header class="masthead">
      <div class="masthead__publication">
        <h1 class="masthead__title">jrgmadrid.</h1>
        <p class="masthead__meta">
          <span>after-hours editorial</span>
          <span aria-hidden="true">·</span>
          <span>no.001</span>
          <span aria-hidden="true">·</span>
          <span>may 2026</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <aside class="masthead__wink" aria-label="masthead note">
        <p>it's a personal site, calm down.<br />lowercase on purpose.</p>
      </aside>
    </header>

    <article class="featured">
      <p class="featured__kicker">feature</p>
      <h2 class="featured__title"><em>the four-stage agent pipeline.</em></h2>
      <div class="featured__body">
        <p>research, plan, implement, verify-and-simplify, with me as the human gate between each. markdown artifacts handed off between subagents. ~40 story points/sprint sustained at spare; built the next iteration on personal time.</p>
        <p>mastra + claude opus. designed to be the thing other people ask about.</p>
      </div>
      <p class="featured__link">
        <a href="https://github.com/jrgmadrid">writeup forthcoming. for now: see the bones on github.</a>
      </p>
    </article>

    <aside class="sidebar" aria-label="currently">
      <h2 class="sidebar__title">currently.</h2>

      <section class="sidebar__group">
        <h3 class="sidebar__label"><em>reading</em></h3>
        <ul class="sidebar__list">
          <li>fredric jameson, <em>postmodernism, or, the cultural logic of late capitalism</em>. archived on the desk for two weeks.</li>
          <li>deleuze + guattari, <em>capitalism and schizophrenia</em>. rhizomes only; the rest can wait.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="sidebar__group">
        <h3 class="sidebar__label"><em>building</em></h3>
        <ul class="sidebar__list">
          <li>this site. you're inside it.</li>
          <li>the four-stage agent pipeline. personal r&amp;d iteration.</li>
          <li>mech tactics: godot 4, fire-emblem-with-robots prototype. gift project; not for sale.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="sidebar__group">
        <h3 class="sidebar__label"><em>watching</em></h3>
        <ul class="sidebar__list">
          <li>yuasa, <em>night is short, walk on girl</em>. third pass this year.</li>
          <li>whatever is on mubi at 11pm.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="sidebar__group">
        <h3 class="sidebar__label"><em>drinking</em></h3>
        <ul class="sidebar__list">
          <li>espresso tonic. oat milk on the side.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </aside>

    <footer class="colophon">
      <div class="colophon__group">
        <p class="colophon__label"><em>this issue</em></p>
        <p>no.001<br />may 2026</p>
      </div>
      <div class="colophon__group">
        <p class="colophon__label"><em>type</em></p>
        <p>canela, commercial type.<br />triplicate, house industries.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="colophon__group">
        <p class="colophon__label"><em>color</em></p>
        <p>night-sky purple, lifted from the riverside scene in yuasa's <em>night is short, walk on girl</em>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="colophon__group">
        <p class="colophon__label"><em>built</em></p>
        <p>astro + tailwind v4. claude wrote first drafts. the page refuses to look like that.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="colophon__group colophon__group--find">
        <p class="colophon__label"><em>find me</em></p>
        <p><a href="https://github.com/jrgmadrid">github.com/jrgmadrid</a></p>
      </div>
    </footer>

  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .spread {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
    grid-template-areas:
      "m m m m m m m m m m m m"
      "f f f f f f f f s s s s"
      "c c c c c c c c c c c c";
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* Masthead --------------------------------------------- */
  .masthead {
    grid-area: m;
    background: var(--color-purple-deep);
    padding: var(--space-3xl) var(--container-padding) var(--space-2xl);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-grid-on-purple);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
    column-gap: var(--grid-gap);
    align-items: end;
    row-gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .masthead__publication {
    grid-column: 1 / 9;
  }

  .masthead__title {
    font-size: var(--text-display);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: var(--leading-display);
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-md) -0.04em;
    color: var(--color-ink-on-purple);
  }

  .masthead__meta {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-small);
    color: var(--color-ink-on-purple-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .masthead__wink {
    grid-column: 9 / -1;
    align-self: end;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: var(--text-subheading);
    color: var(--color-ink-on-purple-muted);
    line-height: var(--leading-heading);
    text-align: right;
    max-width: 28ch;
    margin-left: auto;
  }

  .masthead__wink p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Featured pointer ------------------------------------ */
  .featured {
    grid-area: f;
    background: var(--color-purple-deep);
    padding: var(--space-3xl) var(--container-padding);
    border-right: 1px solid var(--color-grid-on-purple);
    color: var(--color-ink-on-purple);
  }

  .featured__kicker {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-caption);
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    color: var(--color-ink-on-purple-faint);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-lg);
  }

  .featured__title {
    font-size: var(--text-heading);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: var(--leading-heading);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-2xl) -0.03em;
    max-width: 20ch;
    color: var(--color-ink-on-purple);
  }

  .featured__body {
    max-width: 52ch;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .featured__body p {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-body);
    line-height: var(--leading-body);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-md);
    color: var(--color-ink-on-purple);
  }

  .featured__body p:last-child {
    color: var(--color-ink-on-purple-muted);
  }

  .featured__link {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-small);
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-ink-on-purple-muted);
  }

  /* Sidebar -------------------------------------------- */
  .sidebar {
    grid-area: s;
    background: var(--color-cream-paper);
    color: var(--color-ink-on-cream);
    padding: var(--space-3xl) var(--container-padding) var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .sidebar__title {
    font-size: var(--text-heading);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: var(--leading-heading);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-2xl) -0.03em;
    color: var(--color-ink-on-cream);
  }

  .sidebar__group {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .sidebar__group:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .sidebar__label {
    font-size: var(--text-subheading);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm);
    color: var(--color-ink-on-cream-muted);
  }

  .sidebar__list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .sidebar__list li {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-small);
    line-height: var(--leading-body);
    padding: var(--space-sm) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-grid-on-cream);
    color: var(--color-ink-on-cream);
  }

  .sidebar__list li:first-child {
    border-top: none;
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  /* Colophon ------------------------------------------- */
  .colophon {
    grid-area: c;
    background: var(--color-purple-deeper);
    padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--container-padding);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-grid-on-purple);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
    column-gap: var(--grid-gap);
    row-gap: var(--space-lg);
    color: var(--color-ink-on-purple-muted);
  }

  .colophon__group {
    grid-column: span 3;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-small);
    line-height: var(--leading-body);
  }

  .colophon__group p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .colophon__group--find {
    grid-column: 10 / -1;
    text-align: right;
  }

  .colophon__group--find a {
    color: var(--color-ink-on-purple);
  }

  .colophon__label {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: var(--text-small);
    color: var(--color-ink-on-purple-faint);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-xs);
  }

  /* Mobile-different ----------------------------------- */
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .spread {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      grid-template-areas:
        "m"
        "f"
        "s"
        "c";
    }

    .masthead {
      display: block;
      padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--container-padding);
    }

    .masthead__publication,
    .masthead__wink {
      grid-column: auto;
    }

    .masthead__wink {
      text-align: left;
      max-width: none;
      margin: var(--space-lg) 0 0;
      font-size: var(--text-body);
    }

    .featured {
      padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--container-padding);
      border-right: none;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--color-grid-on-purple);
    }

    .featured__title {
      max-width: 18ch;
    }

    .sidebar {
      padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--container-padding);
    }

    .colophon {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      row-gap: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .colophon__group {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
    }

    .colophon__group--find {
      text-align: left;
    }
  }
</style>
